| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0365 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b434c460-c206-5434-9907-701ebb39eb73"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
